{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":895,"text":"TED is 30."},{"time":2543,"text":"The world wide web is celebrating this month"},{"time":5181,"text":"its 25th anniversary."},{"time":7453,"text":"So I've got a question for you."},{"time":10142,"text":"Let's talk about the journey, mainly about the future."},{"time":14966,"text":"Let's talk about the state."},{"time":16681,"text":"Let's talk about what sort of a web we want."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18995,"text":"So 25 years ago, then, I was working at CERN."},{"time":22315,"text":"I got permission in the end after about a year"},{"time":24665,"text":"to basically do it as a side project."},{"time":27297,"text":"I wrote the code."},{"time":28995,"text":"I was I suppose the first user."},{"time":31144,"text":"There was a lot of concern"},{"time":33687,"text":"that people didn't want to pick it up"},{"time":35206,"text":"because it would be too complicated."},{"time":37030,"text":"A lot of persuasion, a lot of wonderful"},{"time":38749,"text":"collaboration with other people,"},{"time":40459,"text":"and bit by bit, it worked."},{"time":42888,"text":"It took off. It was pretty cool."},{"time":44531,"text":"And in fact, a few years later in 2000,"},{"time":47748,"text":"five percent of the world population"},{"time":51950,"text":"were using the world wide web."},{"time":53769,"text":"In 2007, seven years later, 17 percent."},{"time":56480,"text":"In 2008, we formed the World Wide Web Foundation"},{"time":59820,"text":"partly to look at that"},{"time":61394,"text":"and worry about that figure."},{"time":64244,"text":"And now here we are in 2014,"},{"time":66303,"text":"and 40 percent of the world"},{"time":68537,"text":"are using the world wide web, and counting."},{"time":72553,"text":"Obviously it's increasing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74555,"text":"I want you to think about both sides of that."},{"time":77963,"text":"Okay, obviously to anybody here at TED,"},{"time":80180,"text":"the first question you ask is, what can we do"},{"time":83163,"text":"to get the other 60 percent on board"},{"time":85219,"text":"as quickly as possible?"},{"time":86539,"text":"Lots of important things. Obviously\nit's going to be around mobile."},{"time":88854,"text":"But also, I want you to think about the 40 percent,"},{"time":90834,"text":"because if you're sitting there yourself"},{"time":92544,"text":"sort of with a web-enabled life,"},{"time":95170,"text":"you don't remember things anymore,"},{"time":96466,"text":"you just look them up,"},{"time":98180,"text":"then you may feel that it's been a success"},{"time":102263,"text":"and we can all sit back."},{"time":104243,"text":"But in fact, yeah, it's been a success,"},{"time":107326,"text":"there's lots of things, Khan Academy"},{"time":109272,"text":"for crying out loud, there's Wikipedia,"},{"time":111561,"text":"there's a huge number of free e-books"},{"time":113378,"text":"that you can read online,"},{"time":114784,"text":"lots of wonderful things for education,"},{"time":116552,"text":"things in many areas."},{"time":118276,"text":"Online commerce has in some cases"},{"time":120678,"text":"completely turned upside down the\nway commerce works altogether,"},{"time":123469,"text":"made types of commerce available"},{"time":125024,"text":"which weren't available at all before."},{"time":127350,"text":"Commerce has been almost universally affected."},{"time":130732,"text":"Government, not universally affected,"},{"time":132999,"text":"but very affected, and on a good day,"},{"time":135112,"text":"lots of open data, lots of e-government,"},{"time":138080,"text":"so lots of things which are visible"},{"time":140783,"text":"happening on the web."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142411,"text":"Also, lots of things which are less visible."},{"time":144522,"text":"The healthcare, late at night when they're worried"},{"time":146925,"text":"about what sort of cancer"},{"time":148636,"text":"somebody they care about might have,"},{"time":150761,"text":"when they just talk across the Internet to somebody"},{"time":155767,"text":"who they care about very much in another country."},{"time":160276,"text":"Those sorts of things are not, they're not out there,"},{"time":164495,"text":"and in fact they've acquired\na certain amount of privacy."},{"time":167715,"text":"So we cannot assume that part of the web,"},{"time":170499,"text":"part of the deal with the web,"},{"time":171590,"text":"is when I use the web,"},{"time":173026,"text":"it's just a transparent, neutral medium."},{"time":176416,"text":"I can talk to you over it without worrying"},{"time":178952,"text":"about what we in fact now know is happening,"},{"time":181811,"text":"without worrying about the fact"},{"time":184261,"text":"that not only will surveillance be happening"},{"time":186207,"text":"but it'll be done by people who may abuse the data."},{"time":189245,"text":"So in fact, something we realized,"},{"time":190451,"text":"we can't just use the web,"},{"time":191860,"text":"we have to worry about"},{"time":193545,"text":"what the underlying infrastructure of the whole thing,"},{"time":197119,"text":"is it in fact of a quality that we need?"},{"time":201315,"text":"We revel in the fact that we\nhave this wonderful free speech."},{"time":206264,"text":"We can tweet, and oh, lots and lots of people"},{"time":209302,"text":"can see our tweets, except when they can't,"},{"time":212227,"text":"except when actually Twitter\nis blocked from their country,"},{"time":215578,"text":"or in some way the way we try to express ourselves"},{"time":218921,"text":"has put some information\nabout the state of ourselves,"},{"time":221856,"text":"the state of the country we live in,"},{"time":223219,"text":"which isn't available to anybody else."},{"time":225703,"text":"So we must protest and make sure"},{"time":228684,"text":"that censorship is cut down,"},{"time":230808,"text":"that the web is opened up"},{"time":232382,"text":"where there is censorship."}]},{"cues":[{"time":234839,"text":"We love the fact that the web is open."},{"time":237549,"text":"It allows us to talk. Anybody can talk to anybody."},{"time":239754,"text":"It doesn't matter who we are."},{"time":241592,"text":"And then we join these big"},{"time":242929,"text":"social networking companies"},{"time":245582,"text":"which are in fact effectively built as silos,"},{"time":248944,"text":"so that it's much easier to talk to somebody"},{"time":250733,"text":"in the same social network"},{"time":252567,"text":"than it is to talk to somebody in a different one,"},{"time":254890,"text":"so in fact we're sometimes limiting ourselves."},{"time":259264,"text":"And we also have, if you've read\nthe book about the filter bubble,"},{"time":262190,"text":"the filter bubble phenomenon is that"},{"time":264158,"text":"we love to use machines"},{"time":265960,"text":"which help us find stuff we like."},{"time":268092,"text":"So we love it when we're bathed in"},{"time":270434,"text":"what things we like to click on,"},{"time":272166,"text":"and so the machine automatically feeds us"},{"time":274326,"text":"the stuff that we like and we end up"},{"time":275810,"text":"with this rose-colored spectacles view of the world"},{"time":280071,"text":"called a filter bubble."},{"time":282260,"text":"So here are some of the things which maybe"},{"time":284203,"text":"threaten the social web we have."}]},{"cues":[{"time":287295,"text":"What sort of web do you want?"},{"time":289224,"text":"I want one which is not\nfragmented into lots of pieces,"},{"time":292662,"text":"as some countries have been suggesting"},{"time":294845,"text":"they should do in reaction to recent surveillance."},{"time":297945,"text":"I want a web which has got, for example,"},{"time":301628,"text":"is a really good basis for democracy."},{"time":304588,"text":"I want a web where I can use healthcare"},{"time":309165,"text":"with privacy and where there's a lot"},{"time":310920,"text":"of health data, clinical data is available"},{"time":313090,"text":"to scientists to do research."},{"time":315020,"text":"I want a web where the other 60 percent"},{"time":318710,"text":"get on board as fast as possible."},{"time":321050,"text":"I want a web which is such\na powerful basis for innovation"},{"time":325668,"text":"that when something nasty happens,"},{"time":327051,"text":"some disaster strikes, that we can respond"},{"time":329380,"text":"by building stuff to respond to it very quickly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":333160,"text":"So this is just some of the things that I want,"},{"time":336090,"text":"from a big list, obviously it's longer."},{"time":338526,"text":"You have your list."},{"time":339767,"text":"I want us to use this 25th anniversary"},{"time":342541,"text":"to think about what sort of a web we want."},{"time":345534,"text":"You can go to webat25.org"},{"time":347233,"text":"and find some links."},{"time":348236,"text":"There are lots of sites where people"},{"time":349292,"text":"have started to put together a Magna Carta,"},{"time":352004,"text":"a bill of rights for the web."},{"time":353530,"text":"How about we do that?"},{"time":355043,"text":"How about we decide, these are, in a way,"},{"time":359670,"text":"becoming fundamental rights, the right\nto communicate with whom I want."},{"time":363330,"text":"What would be on your list for that Magna Carta?"},{"time":365288,"text":"Let's crowdsource a Magna Carta"},{"time":368156,"text":"for the web."},{"time":370398,"text":"Let's do that this year."},{"time":372490,"text":"Let's use the energy from the 25th anniversary"},{"time":375797,"text":"to crowdsource a Magna Carta"},{"time":378409,"text":"to the web. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":379891,"text":"Thank you. And do me a favor, will you?"},{"time":384397,"text":"Fight for it for me. Okay? Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":386963,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}